<li class="scanner-list" style="padding-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Lightweight:</strong> With some handheld scanner models weighing in at less than 1.5 pounds, portable scanners are designed to make it easy to scan on the go. Most mobile scanners fit easily into a backpack, purse, suitcase, or briefcase.</li>
